Author: reynita1
Text: it’s okay, i was supposed to start a free trial at my local gym this week so i could work out w my friend.... ended up spraining my wrist pretty badly at work, and continued to use it for the next week straight even though i was literally in tears. my friend who’s a nurse confirmed it was a sprain yesterday, and i still can’t really be using it until it heals.  injuries suck dickballs
